## Modifications Made by Muhammad Heikal Iskandar

- ✅ Customized all content, branding, and personal information
- ✅ Added comprehensive SEO schema markup and metadata
- ✅ Enhanced accessibility with ARIA labels and semantic HTML
- ✅ Implemented responsive animations with mobile optimization
- ✅ Updated to Next.js 15 App Router with latest best practices
- ✅ Added dynamic sitemap and robots.txt generation
- ✅ Optimized images with next/image and modern formats (AVIF, WebP)
- ✅ Improved performance with code splitting and lazy loading
- ✅ Added structured data (JSON-LD) for better search engine understanding
- ✅ Updated color schemes, typography, and overall design system

